* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 17:51 Page   1
*                                      EXERC4.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC4.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC4.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.     EX04.
     3 AUTHOR.         EVILLYN.
     4 INSTALLATION.   FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.   18/03/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 18-Mar-25 17:51.
     7 SECURITY. APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.  FATECSP-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.  FATECSP-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT CADCLI1 ASSIGN TO 'CADCLI1.DAT'
    18         ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT CADCLI2 ASSIGN TO 'CADCLI2.DAT'
    20         ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    21
    22 DATA DIVISION.
    23 FILE SECTION.
    24
    25 FD  CADCLI1.
    26 01  REG-ENT.
    27     02 COD-ENT     PIC 9(05).
    28     02 NOME-ENT    PIC X(20).
    29     02 SEXO        PIC X(01).
    30
    31 FD  CADCLI2.
    32 01  REGISTRO-CADCLI2.
    33     02 COD-SAI     PIC 9(05).
    34     02 NOME-SAI    PIC X(20).
    35
    36 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    37 77  FIM-ARQUIVO    PIC X(03) VALUE 'NAO'.
    38 77  CONTINUAR      PIC X VALUE 'Y'.
    39
    40 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    41
    42 EXEMPLO.
    43     PERFORM ABRIR-ARQUIVOS.
    44     PERFORM LEITURA-REGISTROS.
    45     PERFORM FECHAR-ARQUIVOS.
    46     STOP RUN.
    47
    48 ABRIR-ARQUIVOS.
    49     OPEN INPUT CADCLI1
    50          OUTPUT CADCLI2.
    51
    52 LEITURA-REGISTROS.
    53     READ CADCLI1 INTO REG-ENT
    54         AT END
    55             MOVE 'S' TO FIM-ARQUIVO
    56         NOT AT END
    57             IF SEXO OF REG-ENT = 'M'
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 17:51 Page   2
*                                      EXERC4.CBL
    58                 MOVE COD-ENT TO COD-SAI
    59                 MOVE NOME-ENT TO NOME-SAI
    60                 WRITE REGISTRO-CADCLI2
    61             END-IF
    62             IF FIM-ARQUIVO = 'NAO' THEN
    63                 GO TO LEITURA-REGISTROS
    64             END-IF
    65     END-READ.
    66
    67 FECHAR-ARQUIVOS.
    68     CLOSE CADCLI1
    69           CADCLI2.
